ILn8V58vMCTYg">Thái liên - 採蓮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%93ng-V%E1%BB%8Bnh/author-E6a5e7SOI8-d6_k05ZXmwg">Nguyễn Phúc Hồng Vịnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-chu-qu%C3%A1-H%C3%A0-Trung-h%E1%BB%93i-cung-k%C3%BD/poem-Xaj9g70Pnj60t9W3H-b86w">Thị ngự chu quá Hà Trung hồi cung ký - 侍御舟過河中匯恭記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%E1%BB%91ng-b%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh/poem-Wg0ot4FW2PMgi-jPSv_v0g">Tống bắc sứ Sài Trang Khanh - 送北使柴莊卿</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-X3Oume1_mYQvTGcgMAhydQ">Trần Quang Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Truy-v%C3%A3n-S%E1%BA%A7m-L%C3%A2u-thi/poem-seuC8FfokFvaiVGL6Lvmag">Truy vãn Sầm Lâu thi - 追挽岑樓詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Trung-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-n8TXz8ZnEQ2g7U6IvK74Vw">Nguyễn Trung Ngạn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
